# Rock, Paper, Scissors Game

This game was quite simple to make in python code. All it took was some logic and a little bit of planning.

## Requirements to play

- To play the game you have to download python 3.11 if you don't have it.
- Then, run python3 script.py in your Windows or Mac terminal (if you don't know how to, look it up on YouTube)

## How to play Rock, Paper Scissors
You start play either choosing rock, paper or scissors. After the bot will pick randomly from rock, paper scissors.

To determine the winner, follow this list:

- Rock beats Scissors
- Paper beats Rock
- Scissors beats Paper

## About

The python script I created was a portfolio project in a Computer Science course within the website Codecademy. I learned a lot of things of the Codecademy platform when creating these projects.

## Programming Languages Used
- Python 3.11
